<br>
If the kiosk had a Low Light Scope (immediately after the lockpick), it did not have a Yamawhatever Movement Predictor (last item in kiosk).<br>
<br>
Conversely, if the kiosk had Yamawhatever Movement Predictor, it would not have a Low Light Scope.<br>
<br>
It used to be a pretty even toss up as to which one you would get, so maybe you just had several kiosks in a row that had the YMP?<br>
<br>
Of course, FC may have borked the shop inventory again (that seems awfully easy to do, which as a database admin, frightens me...), and maybe the scopes have gone to the same vacation spot that Blessed with Thunder was visiting earlier...<br>
